:: "I told you like an hour ago" {"position":"3600,2700","size":"100,100"}
For this situation we would want to use  ''Stop and Resolve'' 
Stop and Resolve refers to a technique to help individuals stop what they are doing and assess or resolve the situation when they think something isn’t right. 

At this point the focus needs to be on how to get the patient the [[resources they need]]  , not our feeling about the situation .


