:: I heard 10,000 units IVP bolus Heparin, is that correct? {"position":"3250,3200","size":"100,100"}
YES!
It is important to maintain a questioning attitude when receiving an order from a physican while maintaining professionalism. 
A tool that is often used in this scenario is   ''ARCC ''
'(text-style:"bold","underline")['A']'sk a Question –(text-style:"bold","underline")[''R']'equest a Change–v'oice a '(text-style:"bold","underline")['C'']oncern –use your '(text-style:"bold","underline")['C'']hain of Command.

Let's check on that [[order]]


